 the seventeen governorship candidates participating in the Saturday's election in Ondo state have signed a peace pact to ensure violence-free election with a promise to accept its outcome. October 6, 2020 In "Ondo Decides" Dayo Johnson - Akure Ten of the seventeen governorship candidates participating in the Saturday's election in Ondo state have signed a peace pact to ensure a violence-free election with a promise to accept its outcome. The three major candidates that signed the peace accord include, Rotimi Akeredolu of the All… October 6, 2020 In "Politics" Candidate of the Zenith Labour Party governorship candidate, Hon Agboola Ajayi has said that security arrangement in today's election has been compromised. Ajayi said this after casting his vote about 10.32 a.m at Apoi Ward II, Unit 004 in the 2020 Ondo governorship election. He lauded the large turnout of… October 10, 2020 In "News"